ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This course provides an opportunity to learn about your colleagues' research in a professional, but laid back setting. I do recommend this course to others, because it provides the opportunity for intellectual expansion and research help from your peers. I do miss the coffee though.....

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Yes because it forces me to put a coherent story about my research together every year.
Good opportunity to learn about the diversity of projects going on in the department and what types of technology/methods are easily available.
